s32v I2C manager

%C [options]

Options:
    -I interface        (1 | 2 | 3 , Default: 1)
    -p addr             I2C base address
    -i irq              I2C interrupt
    -c clock            Input clock (default: 133000000)
    -v                  set verbose

Generic options:
    --b bus_speed       Default bus speed. (Default: 100000)
    --m max_msg_len     Minimum length of resmgr receive buffer. (Default: 128 bytes)
    --n nparts          Minimum number of iov_t's in resmgr context. (Default: 2)
    --u unit            Unit number. Number to append to device name prefix (/dev/i2c). (Default: 0)

    i2c-s32v -I1 --u1
